fix: personalized home page no longer crashes on rerank failure

- rerank.ts: loosen RerankSchema bounds (blurb 4-220, reason 10-600)
  so a slightly-too-long LLM blurb no longer triggers a Zod validation
  error that bubbles up as a Server Components render error.
- rerank.ts: wrap generateObject() in try/catch with a deterministic
  template fallback (uses summary_zh + judgment_zh from each candidate).
  Trim blurbs at 60 chars on the consumer side.
- page.tsx: wrap getPersonalizedFeed() in try/catch; on any failure,
  fall back to the anonymous feed instead of crashing.
